## ✅ Feature 1: AI Trust System & Performance Ranking

### Backend
- **`UserService.recalculateTrustScore(Long providerId)`** — calculates:
  - **Completion Rate** = completed bookings / total bookings
  - **Cancellation Rate** = cancelled bookings / total bookings
  - **On-Time Performance** = heuristic: `100 - (cancellationRate × 0.5)`
  - **Trust Score** = [(completionRate × 0.7) + (onTimePerformance × 0.3)](file:///c:/Users/pruthviraj/OneDrive/Desktop/jdk/LocalConnect/backend/src/main/java/com/nearnest/model/User.java#11-316), capped 0–100
- **[BookingService](file:///c:/Users/pruthviraj/OneDrive/Desktop/jdk/LocalConnect/backend/src/main/java/com/nearnest/service/BookingService.java#21-248)** — triggers recalculation on COMPLETED or CANCELLED status changes
- **`ServiceService.searchServices()`** — now sorts by `provider.trustScore DESC` by default

### Frontend
- **[ServiceCard.js](file:///c:/Users/pruthviraj/OneDrive/Desktop/jdk/LocalConnect/frontend/src/components/ServiceCard.js)** — displays an indigo `Trust N` badge next to the category tag
- **[ServiceDetails.js](file:///c:/Users/pruthviraj/OneDrive/Desktop/jdk/LocalConnect/frontend/src/pages/ServiceDetails.js)** — shows a green Trust Score pill `🛡 Trust Score: N` inside the provider spotlight
- **[ProviderProfile.js](file:///c:/Users/pruthviraj/OneDrive/Desktop/jdk/LocalConnect/frontend/src/pages/ProviderProfile.js)** — shows the trust score badge alongside the provider name

